        <h1>Fitness Plan (40-65 Overweight)</h1>
        
        <h2>Diet Plan</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Breakfast:</strong> Green smoothie (spinach, banana, almond milk, chia seeds).</li>
            <li><strong>Lunch:</strong> Baked salmon with steamed greens and quinoa.</li>
            <li><strong>Snacks:</strong> Handful of mixed nuts or hummus with carrot sticks.</li>
            <li><strong>Dinner:</strong> Grilled chicken with a fresh salad and olive oil dressing.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Gym Routine</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Low-impact cardio (walking, elliptical) for 30-40 minutes daily.</li>
            <li>Light strength training 3 times a week (resistance bands, dumbbells).</li>
            <li>Core stability and stretching exercises (yoga, Pilates).</li>
        </ul>
